*Suviše* je dugo trajalo tiho ćutanje. (The silence lasted too long.)

Ona je *suviše* jaka da bi je bilo ko pobedio. (She is too strong for anyone to defeat her.)

*Suviše* je malo vremena da se sve obavi. (There is not enough time to do it all.)

Njegova novčana naknada bila je *suviše* mala. (His financial compensation was too small.)

Njegov argument je *suviše* slab da bi bilo ozbiljno uzet u obzir. (His argument is too weak to be taken seriously.)

*Suviše* malo ljudi zna za tu tajnu. (Too few people know about that secret.)

*Suviše* je ljudi koji vole da se ponašaju neprimereno. (There are too many people who like to behave inappropriately.)